A shot for every "ugh I love Sandra but wheeeeen is Jodie getting her awaaaard" this is wiiild
Like first of all they're either...
body:
A shot for every “ugh I love Sandra but wheeeeen is Jodie getting her awaaaard” this is wiiild

Like first of all they’re either on the same category or Jodie wasn’t nominated and why’s that cause ofc a show with ONE season so far is only going to get nominated with the best known actress and that’s Sandra Oh.

I’m not gonna get into who’s better tho it seems you do every time you make a fucking post like that

And it’s not like it has been happening for years? It’s not like it’s gonna be Jodie’s last chance at winning and she’s been snubbed repeatedly like Keri Russell has, now THAT’S a perfect snubbing example. Like, now everybody knows about Jodie, they didn’t in the past now they do, and they’ll pay more attention and now that Killing Eve is mainstream and Jodie more popular shell get nominated and probably win in coming seasons

Anyway stop shitting on Sandra just cause she’s finally getting attention and let us enjoy her wins
